        {
            "title": "川普警告伊朗時間所剩無幾 美軍艦艇進入該地區",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普警告伊朗，與美國達成協議的時間已經所剩不多，並表示一支進入該地區的美國軍艦編隊已準備好「以速度和迅猛之勢」完成任務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在一則社交媒體帖子中表示，他希望伊朗回到談判桌前，就一項「公平公正的協議 —— 不能有核武器」展開談判，並稱一旦發生攻擊，其規模和後果將遠超他去年6月下令對伊朗核計畫發動的打擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普多次警告稱，美國可能再次對伊朗發動攻擊，不過此前這些威脅與伊朗鎮壓抗議行動相關。川普此前還表示，伊朗核計畫已在去年6月的打擊中被「徹底摧毀」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-460fd2c2-0787-30c2-94b5-654842df8ece-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普的最新表態推動原油價格升至日內高點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周一，伊朗半官方媒體伊朗學生通訊社報導稱，伊朗外交部長阿拉格齊與美國特使威特科夫以「非正式」方式互相傳遞信息。在緊張局勢不斷升級之際，已有多個國家提出願意在美伊之間進行斡旋。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著亞伯拉罕·林肯號航空母艦及其打擊群近日進入該地區，外界對美國可能即將再次發動攻擊的猜測進一步升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Warns Iran That Time is Running Out as Ships Enter Region</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E6%89%80%E5%89%A9%E7%84%A1%E5%B9%BE-%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E8%89%87%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E8%A9%B2%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80-131000612.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 23:18:13",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Rieder曾向川普對手和民主黨高層捐款 恐給競逐聯儲會主席添波折",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Christopher Goodney/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HUEW8JINt2mFf0p3hNZKyQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/989c75f397c7832d90bfa80ea5d1e281\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Christopher Goodney/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國聯邦選舉委員會(FEC)的記錄顯示，被視為下一任聯儲會主席熱門人選的貝萊德高管Rick Rieder曾向唐納德·川普的一些主要政治對手和<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:民主黨;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/民主黨\">民主黨</a>高層捐款。這段歷史有可能考驗川普青睞任用忠誠派的用人傾向。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據符合Rieder姓名和雇主信息的FEC數據，Rieder的捐款歷史悠久且涉及美國兩黨，包括2024年支持妮基·黑莉的總統競選、2020年支持民主黨人Pete Buttigieg和Cory Booker，以及2016年支持Jeb Bush參選等。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-20d77cd9-51b4-3c81-9555-fde3dbcc442c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">FEC的記錄顯示，Rieder在2016年、2020年和2024年川普三次參選期間，均未向他提供支持。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Rick Rieder攝影：克里斯托弗·古德尼/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3_aQaVl7.WRcF1cxUYCpPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9f7b5aa433a1de7f5bab7b04a0a76b5a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Rick Rieder攝影：克里斯托弗·古德尼/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最近幾周，Rieder競逐下一任聯儲會主席的勢頭有所增強：他憑借改造聯儲會的設想，以及在華爾街的資歷，給川普留下了深刻印象。但過往的捐款記錄可能令他的競逐之路出現波折，也凸顯川普在尋找一位各項條件都符合的人選時所面臨的兩難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相關記錄顯示，Rieder曾向參議院民主黨領袖Chuck Schumer、眾議院民主黨領袖Hakeem Jeffries或他們的關聯團體捐款，兩人均為紐約州民主黨人。FEC申報信息還顯示，Rieder登記的地址位於紐約州和紐澤西州。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還曾向其他溫和派民主黨人捐款，包括弗吉尼亞州參議員Mark Warner，以及前參議員Jon Tester和Sherrod Brown；同時也向一些共和黨人捐款，這些人長期在川普派系的共和黨內失寵並已退出政壇，其中包括Mitt Romney和Paul Ryan。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rieder及貝萊德的代表不予置評，但並未否認上述捐款情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Rieder Donations to MAGA Rivals Tests Trump’s Fed Chair Demands</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Christopher Condon、Silla Brush.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/rieder%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE-%E6%81%90%E7%B5%A6%E7%AB%B6%E9%80%90%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%B7%BB%E6%B3%A2%E6%8A%98-143930552.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 23:33:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "明尼阿波利斯市長稱不會改變移民政策 川普指責其「在玩火」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 川普痛批<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:明尼阿波利斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/明尼阿波利斯\">明尼阿波利斯</a>市長Jacob Frey。這位市長早前表示，不會為了換取聯邦特工的撤離而改變該市的移民政策，這令聯邦與地方領導人之間本已脆弱的關係緩和再添變數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他核心圈子裡有人能解釋一下嗎？這種說法嚴重違反了法律，他這是在玩火！」川普周三在社交媒體上發帖說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Frey周二表示，他已告知川普的邊境事務負責人湯姆·霍曼「明尼阿波利斯現在不會、未來也不會執行聯邦移民法」，並向他介紹了「此次行動對明尼阿波利斯及其周邊社區造成的嚴重負面影響」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eceb45b7-122c-32ec-bb25-5459eb23d69c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普已更換移民驅逐行動的指揮層，派遣霍曼前往明尼阿波利斯，以緩和該市的緊張局勢。此前，聯邦官員在該市抗議驅逐浪潮的街頭示威活動中殺害了兩名美國公民。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Warns Minneapolis Mayor Over Immigration Comments</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
