        {
            "title": "美國抵押貸款利率四周來首次上升 購房及再融資活動承壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:抵押貸款;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/抵押貸款\">抵押貸款</a>利率四周來首次上升，導致購房和再融資活動自年初以來的升勢遇阻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國抵押貸款銀行家協會（MBA）周三公佈的數據顯示，截至1月23日當周，30年期抵押貸款合約利率上升8個基點，至6.24%。此前一周，住房融資成本降至2024年9月以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該協會的購房抵押貸款申請指數上周由三年高點回落0.4%。再融資申請大跌15.7%，為今年以來首次下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">活動降溫表明，在可負擔性約束仍存的情況下，潛在購房者對抵押貸款利率的變動依然敏感。住房融資成本與美國國債市場走勢密切相關，本周早些時候，在日本國債暴跌及地緣政治擔憂背景下，美國10年期國債殖利率躍升。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6e054bb8-00bc-34b9-a932-93e53fea1913-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MBA自1990年以來每周進行這項調查，使用來自抵押貸款銀行家、商業銀行和儲蓄機構的反饋。該數據涵蓋了美國所有零售住宅抵押貸款申請的75%以上。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Mortgage Rates Increase for First Time in Four Weeks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%9B%9B%E5%91%A8%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%BF%E5%8F%8A%E5%86%8D%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%87%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%89%BF%E5%A3%93-123811261.html",
