        {
            "title": "香港外匯基金去年斬獲420億美元投資收益 創歷年最高紀錄",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"香港外匯基金去年斬獲420億美元投資收益 創歷年最高紀錄\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cRcjemVv.oZbaAWRFlbTGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/03c82ba0-fc3d-11f0-b73a-e086e191878c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">香港外匯基金去年斬獲420億美元投資收益 創歷年最高紀錄</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
